cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI 

This paper deals with the problem of multi-label classification, which is a common task in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper proposes a unified margin view to revisit eleven performance measures in multi-label classification, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of performance measures in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR), as well as natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
